[0.000, "o", "rm Module's (TPM) Platform Configuration Register (PCR)\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[0;90m\u001b[0;38:5:245m░░\u001b[0m \u001b[0;32m11, on banks sha1, has been extended with the string 'ready'.\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[0;90m\u001b[0;38:5:245m░░\u001b[0m \u001b[0;32m\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[0;90m\u001b[0;38:5:245m░░\u001b[0m \u001b[0;32mSystem state, configuration and properties are cryptographically measured into\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[0;90m\u001b[0;38:5:245m░░\u001b[0m \u001b[0;32mthe security chip in an irreversible way to provide local and remote\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[0;90m\u001b[0;38:5:245m░░\u001b[0m \u001b[0;32mattestation of system state and identity.\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[0;90m\u001b[0;38:5:245m░░\u001b[0m \u001b[0;32m\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[0;90m\u001b[0;38:5:245m░░\u001b[0m \u001b[0;32mFor example, whenever the system transitions to a new runtime phase, the\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[0;90m\u001b[0;38:5:245m░░\u001b[0m \u001b[0;32mPCRs ares extended with a different string, to ensure that security\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[0;90m\u001b[0;38:5:245m░░\u001b[0m \u001b[0;32mpolicies for TPM-bound secrets and other resources are limited to specific\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[0;90m\u001b[0;38:5:245m░░\u001b[0m \u001b[0;32mphases of the runtime.\u001b[0m\r\nMay 28 13:51:04 sank systemd[1]: Finished TPM PCR Barrier (User).\r\n\u001b[0;90m\u001b[0;38:5:245m░░ \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32mSubject: A start job for unit systemd-pcrphase.service has finished successfully\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[0;90m\u001b[0;38:5:245m░░\u001b[0m \u001b[0;32mDefined-By: systemd\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[0;90m\u001b[0;38:5:245m░░\u001b[0m \u001b[0;32mSupport: https://lists.freedesktop.org/mailman/listinfo/systemd-devel\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[0;90m\u001b[0;38:5:245m░░\u001b[0m \u001b[0;32m\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[0;90m\u001b[0;38:5:245m░░\u001b[0m \u001b[0;32mA start job for unit systemd-pcrphase.service has finished successfully.\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[0;90m\u001b[0;38:5:245m░░\u001b[0m \u001b[0;32m\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[0;90m\u001b[0;38:5:245m░░\u001b[0m \u001b[0;32m